00:04:19.800 --> 00:04:24.940
Um, and the book focuses
quite a bit on, uh,

00:04:24.940 --> 00:04:26.530 position:56%
the heroes who did not make it home.

00:04:26.530 --> 00:04:30.810
Um, but Ed, uh, is a hero who
