00:04:55.500 --> 00:04:56.800
because he was, um, going

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:58.760
to have two Purple
Hearts, but only one scar.

00:04:58.760 --> 00:05:01.710
Uh, which he thought was not fair.

00:05:01.710 --> 00:05:06.580
Um, but after the battle, he was
