good looking corpsman.

00:30:13.410 --> 00:30:15.390
And he just walked up to me.

00:30:15.390 --> 00:30:18.030
He was as normal as could be and
he said, "Why are you doing this?"

00:30:18.030 --> 00:30:19.520
And I said, "Well, it's
the right thing to do."

00:30:19.520 --> 00:30:21.980
