on his 5th deployment.

00:43:17.920 --> 00:43:22.970 position:56%
And he definitely had PTSD, but at
that time he just went ahead anyway.

00:43:22.970 --> 00:43:24.270
We graduated him early.

00:43:24.270 --> 00:43:25.650
About that time my phone rang.

00:43:25.650 --> 00:43:30.650
I had a friend of mine in DC
