00:44:31.400 --> 00:44:35.420
to read a letter to the court at
the end of their, uh, graduation.

00:44:35.420 --> 00:44:36.820
Twenty of them indicated

00:44:36.820 --> 00:44:39.220
on the record they would
have committed suicide

00:44:39.220 --> 00:44:41.320
but for this program.

00:44:41.320 --> 00:44:43.210
So it's been an incredible
event for me,

00:44:43.210 --> 00:44:45.840
an incredible honor
to be with this panel.

00:44:45.840 --> 00:44:47.140
And I'm being sandwiched

00:44:47.140 --> 00:44:52.310
between these two Vietnam
vets, I feel somewhat small.

