Um, I'm Tom Berger.

00:44:56.280 --> 00:44:57.580
Um --

00:44:57.580 --> 00:44:58.920
&gt;&gt; Dr. Tom Berger.

00:44:58.920 --> 00:45:04.620
&gt;&gt; Tom Berger: I am the, uh,
son of two World War II vets.

00:45:04.620 --> 00:45:09.000
My father was with Carlson's
Raiders, a Marine battalion,

00:45:09.000 --> 00:45:10.300
