00:45:10.300 --> 00:45:14.560
And by the time he got to the
states, the Marines, at that time,

00:45:14.560 --> 00:45:18.220
sent their wounded in the
Pacific to Balboa Hospital

00:45:18.220 --> 00:45:20.780
