00:45:26.860 --> 00:45:30.270
that was very attuned
to military service.

00:45:30.270 --> 00:45:35.840 position:56%
Not only my parents, my grandparents
on both sides served in World War I.

00:45:35.840 --> 00:45:42.550 position:56%
In fact, my paternal grandfather was
a tanker in World War I with Patton

00:45:42.550 --> 00:45:48.260
