a dishonorable or other

01:01:02.850 --> 01:01:04.970
than honorable or awaiting
discharge.

01:01:04.970 --> 01:01:06.430
Um, families wrecked.

01:01:06.430 --> 01:01:08.940
Um, they're just a shell
