01:02:29.830 --> 01:02:32.990
I had gotten so much
medication from the VA and I --

01:02:32.990 --> 01:02:36.530
I'd abused them and I just was
tired of feeling like that.

01:02:36.530 --> 01:02:38.050
I felt vulnerable in population

01:02:38.050 --> 01:02:40.130
