01:41:12.140 --> 01:41:14.310
through certain things
in their lives.

01:41:14.310 --> 01:41:16.640
We need to keep coming
together as a community,

01:41:16.640 --> 01:41:19.910
as a nation, um to combat this.

01:41:19.910 --> 01:41:21.210
We need to stick together.

01:41:21.210 --> 01:41:22.510
We need to educate ourselves.

01:41:22.510 --> 01:41:25.840
Everybody needs to be educated
in this area, in -- in --

01:41:25.840 --> 01:41:28.920
in veterans' issues,
if we want to succeed.

